{"tid":61384,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[跨年徒步撚]上水->將軍澳","createTime":"2016-12-31T07:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T09:27:27.000Z","uid":13586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"193636514bf1189e3b59c9b02d38bec56659aa8b","tid":61384,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:50:27.000Z","msg":"本身一直都有種衝動想試下行路or踩單車環港遊，但一直礙於又要返工又要返學，抽唔到時間<br />\n<br />\n另外，唔係特登揀呢d日子，冇特別意思，只係毒撚冇人陪，寄情於景物，好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果懶係要上位咁，要上位神早人字拖上蚺蛇尖啦<br />\n<br />\n大約路線：<br />\n上水火車站出發&gt;粉嶺&gt;沿火車行到大圍（休息用）&gt;折返上馬鞍山&gt;西貢&gt;將軍澳<br />\n<br />\n裝備：<br />\n袋<br />\n兩個奶媽<br />\nMac機<br />\nUsb線 for iPhone <br />\n3ds連藍寶石<br />\n消化餅一筒<br />\n水（邊行邊買）<br />\n紙筆（慣左）<br />\niPhone 裝左runtastic（紀錄路線用，明明for跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n每10分鐘上一上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/31/154648_a3036479790c13af5fb79c1e197807ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F31%2F154648_a3036479790c13af5fb79c1e197807ad.jpg&h=7e19012c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/31/154652_aa7ab9a8b3fd87b83fb4886a5e70e4f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F31%2F154652_aa7ab9a8b3fd87b83fb4886a5e70e4f5.jpg&h=ea46572e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新年都仲咁多蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7edcabc750ae6154b6fc4edb9f9c6182a5deba","tid":61384,"uid":52918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:53:13.000Z","msg":"等你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n唔好渴死,最近好乾,飲多啲水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56a9e266f477d43148d5782b5a57825d413eb0b","tid":61384,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n唔好渴死,最近好乾,飲多啲水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉去活動台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係活動台啱d"},{"pid":"9db8f80fab2c48aff1f677d11472f5b456c2c118","tid":61384,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:24:13.000Z","msg":"唔好行到大圍喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n城門河有橋就好過<br />\n西沙路上斜落斜都要體力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋夜晚新西貢公路好暗<br />\n自己要小心<br />\n<br />\n利申：行過粉嶺-將軍澳"},{"pid":"47a97fad513baa7c894a2c3486aa42b5ada1a3a6","tid":61384,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:36:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好行到大圍喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n城門河有橋就好過<br />\n西沙路上斜落斜都要體力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋夜晚新西貢公路好暗<br />\n自己要小心<br />\n<br />\n利申：行過粉嶺-將軍澳</blockquote><br />\n個次行左幾耐？"},{"pid":"9f7b74b19ab1bf74eef4cff07c14a5d3e6de9dc1","tid":61384,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:55:11.000Z","msg":"留名參考"},{"pid":"ee21821404d0ee170718b015aabf79239a15f8ae","tid":61384,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T09:03:54.000Z","msg":"［行路撚］上水-&gt;將軍澳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/61388?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/61388?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n傳送門"},{"pid":"e5e36e9f3b16be131e5f4caf4cc5b3f0cc087028","tid":61384,"uid":30856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi